{"tid":2493794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲臘親王以皇家海軍中尉身份，乘HMS Whelp艦接受日本投降，重光香港","createTime":"2021-04-18T07:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T09:40:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"051aad0ade6da76333c839739d44b9511245d104","tid":2493794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/vg3xotrv.luowqxt333t.1rxefu1clhc.2ht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fvg3xotrv.luowqxt333t.1rxefu1clhc.2ht.jpg&h=f8993977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【菲臘親王逝世】多次來港訪問，曾協助香港重光<br />\n<br />\n英國白金漢宮宣布，王夫菲臘親王逝世，享年99歲。英國王夫菲臘親王出生於1921年，是希臘及丹麥王子，他的祖父便是跟隨俄國沙皇尼古拉二世來港的希臘國王喬治一世。<br />\n<br />\n菲臘親王在二次大戰曾在皇家海軍服役，先後在地中海及法國南部作戰。在大戰最後階段，他在鄒龍號（HMS Whelp）參與沖繩戰役和日本投降。<br />\n<br />\n之後他便隨鄒龍號來到香港，協助香港重光。據親王回憶，在日本駛住香港途中是他最高興旅程之一，因為他們不用再關燈，也可以打開舷窗，甚至可以沖涼。<br />\n<br />\n在1959年，菲臘親王代表皇室訪問香港。他亦感慨香港戰後發展迅速，與他14年前來時已大大不同。"},{"pid":"c361ea810ccd2bbf206baffca89388eb4b937d5c","tid":2493794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313eeb5a68a6a46709d281c0d8ee22f47151e0b1","tid":2493794,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:38:15.000Z","msg":"God save the queen <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbfaa717fcbb8738d8fa8394b95089e28f3bfbc","tid":2493794,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"佢係好人嚟"},{"pid":"7ebf351816a83e91f7c4ae26afd49324d6ec4234","tid":2493794,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bbfaa717fcbb8738d8fa8394b95089e28f3bfbc","tid":2493794,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"佢係好人嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"但佢長命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}